<body>
<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0134a" xml:id="I01.0052.0134a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0134a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 52</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0134a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>比丘道<g ref="#CB07018"/>造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0134a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0134a0101">大魏武定七年歲次己巳四月丙戌朔四月八日癸巳　司州魏郡易陽人今為武安龍山寺主比丘道<g ref="#CB07018"/>記</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0134b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0134b0101">夫萬相具朗。非有非無。是非雙寂。人莫知其元。所以然者。皆由積善空<note n="0134001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30783"/>＝王【史】</note><note n="0134001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30783"/>【佛拓】，王【史】</note><app n="0134001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">王</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30783"/></rdg></app><note n="0134002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02442"/>＝之【史】</note><note n="0134002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02442"/>【佛拓】，之【史】</note><app n="0134002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02442"/></rdg></app>前。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b02" type="honorific"/><note n="0134003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB25812"/>＝苦【史】</note><note n="0134003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB25812"/>【佛拓】，苦【史】</note><app n="0134003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB25812"/></rdg></app>行授記<app type="star" corresp="#0134002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02442"/></rdg></app>後。便能絜真見樹。定想三九。亦能麾五指以伏狂<note n="0134004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30785"/>＝象【史】</note><note n="0134004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30785"/>【佛拓】，象【史】</note><app n="0134004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">象</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30785"/></rdg></app>。併鬼<note n="0134005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB24980"/>＝王【史】</note><note n="0134005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB24980"/>【佛拓】，王【史】</note><app n="0134005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">王</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB24980"/></rdg></app>於壙
<lb ed="I" n="0134b03" type="honorific"/>野。把火龍而盤掌。指熾焱而為長流。特挺孤秀。英奇<note n="0134006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30811"/>＝若【史】</note><note n="0134006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30811"/>【佛拓】，若【史】</note><app n="0134006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30811"/></rdg></app>此。遉顯伏致滅者矣。況
<lb ed="I" n="0134b04" type="honorific"/>聚沙<note n="0134007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB15626"/>＝泡【史】</note><note n="0134007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB15626"/>【佛拓】，泡【史】</note><app n="0134007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">泡</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB15626"/></rdg></app>沫。寧無壞乎。是以此法師。名道諱<g ref="#CB07018"/>。迺承波長漢。赤龍之胤。元在河<note n="0134008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">閒＝間【史】</note><note n="0134008" resp="ihp" type="mod">閒【佛拓】，間【史】</note><app n="0134008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">間</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">閒</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b05" type="honorific"/>今寄<note n="0134009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB05464"/>＝居【史】</note><note n="0134009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB05464"/>【佛拓】，居【史】</note><app n="0134009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">居</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB05464"/></rdg></app>易陽人也。<note n="0134010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30788"/>＝棄【史】</note><note n="0134010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30788"/>【佛拓】，棄【史】</note><app n="0134010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">棄</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30788"/></rdg></app><note n="0134011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30789"/>＝彼【史】</note><note n="0134011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30789"/>【佛拓】，彼【史】</note><app n="0134011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30789"/></rdg></app>宮城。割愛辭<note n="0134012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30790"/>＝親【史】</note><note n="0134012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30790"/>【佛拓】，親【史】</note><app n="0134012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">親</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30790"/></rdg></app>。倍加韶響。非情所翫。遂寫素<note n="0134013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30791"/>＝服【史】</note><note n="0134013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30791"/>【佛拓】，服【史】</note><app n="0134013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">服</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30791"/></rdg></app>。懃心道
<lb ed="I" n="0134b06" type="honorific"/>君。雖同生滅。遠鑒始<note n="0134014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30792"/>＝終【史】</note><note n="0134014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30792"/>【佛拓】，終【史】</note><app n="0134014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">終</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30792"/></rdg></app>。古今競曉。絜行桑門。纖理靡損。持<note n="0134015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB13806"/>＝禁【史】</note><note n="0134015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB13806"/>【佛拓】，禁【史】</note><app n="0134015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禁</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB13806"/></rdg></app>帶浮。罹剎<note n="0134016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30813"/>＝杜【史】</note><note n="0134016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30813"/>【佛拓】，杜【史】</note><app n="0134016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">杜</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30813"/></rdg></app>塞。懼
<lb ed="I" n="0134b07" type="honorific"/>念傷蘭。<note n="0134017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30793"/>＝斷【史】</note><note n="0134017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30793"/>【佛拓】，斷【史】</note><app n="0134017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">斷</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30793"/></rdg></app><note n="0134018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB03288"/>＝息【史】</note><note n="0134018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB03288"/>【佛拓】，息【史】</note><app n="0134018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">息</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB03288"/></rdg></app><note n="0134019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30794"/>＝繼【史】</note><note n="0134019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30794"/>【佛拓】，繼【史】</note><app n="0134019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">繼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30794"/></rdg></app>草。清清志絜。春松無以侔其鮮。<note n="0134020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB05471"/>＝希【史】</note><note n="0134020" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB05471"/>【佛拓】，希【史】</note><app n="0134020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">希</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB05471"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0134020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">希</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB05471"/></rdg></app>獨<note n="0134021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30795"/>＝穎【史】</note><note n="0134021" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30795"/>【佛拓】，穎【史】</note><app n="0134021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穎</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30795"/></rdg></app>。夜炬無以匹其照。方
<lb ed="I" n="0134b08" type="honorific"/>欲<note n="0134022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30814"/>＝拔【史】</note><note n="0134022" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30814"/>【佛拓】，拔【史】</note><app n="0134022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拔</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30814"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0134003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB25812"/></rdg></app>窟<note n="0134023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30796"/>＝宅【史】</note><note n="0134023" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30796"/>【佛拓】，宅【史】</note><app n="0134023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">宅</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30796"/></rdg></app>。雲昇<note n="0134024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">佊＝彼【史】</note><note n="0134024" resp="ihp" type="mod">佊【佛拓】，彼【史】</note><app n="0134024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">佊</rdg></app>岸。都不復以世慕為榮也。便率<app type="star" corresp="#0134011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30789"/></rdg></app>英傑。信心令儁一百餘
<lb ed="I" n="0134b09" type="honorific"/>人。共<note n="0134025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30815"/>＝裁【史】</note><note n="0134025" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30815"/>【佛拓】，裁【史】</note><app n="0134025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">裁</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30815"/></rdg></app>己貴。同尊上道。且使育王盡藏。須達傾珍。無以比其福。即乃運石荊巖。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b10" type="honorific"/>左置文碑。右法勇塔。雕錯漏彩。連剋聖容之質。狀如真見。晌<g ref="#CB30782"/><note n="0134026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30812"/>＝若【史】</note><note n="0134026" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30812"/>【佛拓】，若【史】</note><app n="0134026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30812"/></rdg></app>丹霞<note n="0134027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30798"/>＝之【史】</note><note n="0134027" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30798"/>【佛拓】，之【史】</note><app n="0134027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30798"/></rdg></app>斑。<note n="0134028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30799"/>＝金【史】</note><note n="0134028" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30799"/>【佛拓】，金【史】</note><app n="0134028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30799"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0134b11" type="honorific"/>瓔<note n="0134029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30800"/>＝向【史】</note><note n="0134029" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30800"/>【佛拓】，向【史】</note><app n="0134029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">向</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30800"/></rdg></app><g ref="#CB30823"/>。如曜靈<app type="star" corresp="#0134002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02442"/></rdg></app>入魚淵。兼下神蔡。奇章<note n="0134030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30801"/>＝顯【史】</note><note n="0134030" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30801"/>【佛拓】，顯【史】</note><app n="0134030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30801"/></rdg></app>分。亦<note n="0134031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30802"/>＝治【史】</note><note n="0134031" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30802"/>【佛拓】，治【史】</note><app n="0134031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">治</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30802"/></rdg></app>形<note n="0134032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30803"/>＝影【史】</note><note n="0134032" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30803"/>【佛拓】，影【史】</note><app n="0134032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">影</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30803"/></rdg></app>。漢朝感夢。宋君偤勇。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b12" type="honorific"/>陵風拊伏。<note n="0134033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30797"/>＝若【史】</note><note n="0134033" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30797"/>【佛拓】，若【史】</note><app n="0134033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30797"/></rdg></app>真鎮神川於中<note n="0134034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00527"/>＝庭【史】</note><note n="0134034" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00527"/>【佛拓】，庭【史】</note><app n="0134034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">庭</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00527"/></rdg></app>。顯志長衢。遊人之矚目者也。珞珞<app type="star" corresp="#0134033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30797"/></rdg></app>七<note n="0134035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30816"/>＝星【史】</note><note n="0134035" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30816"/>【佛拓】，星【史】</note><app n="0134035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">星</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30816"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0134002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02442"/></rdg></app>紀
<lb ed="I" n="0134b13" type="honorific"/><note n="0134036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30804"/>＝天【史】</note><note n="0134036" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30804"/>【佛拓】，天【史】</note><app n="0134036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">天</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30804"/></rdg></app>。巖巖如五岳<app type="star" corresp="#0134002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02442"/></rdg></app><note n="0134037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30805"/>＝綱【史】</note><note n="0134037" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30805"/>【佛拓】，綱【史】</note><app n="0134037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">綱</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30805"/></rdg></app>地。馨風遐振。<note n="0134038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB03140"/>＝璨【史】</note><note n="0134038" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB03140"/>【佛拓】，璨【史】</note><app n="0134038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璨</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB03140"/></rdg></app>爛<note n="0134039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30394"/>＝彌【史】</note><note n="0134039" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30394"/>【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0134039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30394"/></rdg></app>遠。聲霑北<note n="0134040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB13426"/>＝海【史】</note><note n="0134040" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB13426"/>【佛拓】，海【史】</note><app n="0134040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">海</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB13426"/></rdg></app>。飛嚮南冥。故為作頌曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b14" type="honorific"/><note n="0134041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB12752"/>＝彌【史】</note><note n="0134041" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB12752"/>【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0134041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB12752"/></rdg></app>劫長遠。積善空<app type="star" corresp="#0134005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">王</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB24980"/></rdg></app>。行端万有。難比難方。散髮要請。必求所<note n="0134042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30807"/>＝長【史】</note><note n="0134042" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30807"/>【佛拓】，長【史】</note><app n="0134042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">長</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30807"/></rdg></app>。<app type="star" corresp="#0134003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB25812"/></rdg></app>行二三。銘記
<lb ed="I" n="0134b15" type="honorific"/>定光。世雄無匹。廣救一<note n="0134043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">仞＝切【史】</note><note n="0134043" resp="ihp" type="mod">仞【佛拓】，切【史】</note><app n="0134043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">切</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">仞</rdg></app>。五指現師。狂<app type="star" corresp="#0134004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">象</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30785"/></rdg></app><note n="0134044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30806"/>＝乃【史】</note><note n="0134044" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30806"/>【佛拓】，乃【史】</note><app n="0134044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">乃</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30806"/></rdg></app>滯。伏鬼壙野。兩<note n="0134045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">炏＝炎【史】</note><note n="0134045" resp="ihp" type="mod">炏【佛拓】，炎【史】</note><app n="0134045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">炎</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">炏</rdg></app>同翳。舍利乃悟。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b16" type="honorific"/>人生得<note n="0134046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB09497"/>＝濟【史】</note><note n="0134046" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB09497"/>【佛拓】，濟【史】</note><app n="0134046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">濟</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB09497"/></rdg></app>。熾火冰流。咸獲淨地。沙門清潔。規<note n="0134047" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30817"/>＝矩【史】</note><note n="0134047" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30817"/>【佛拓】，矩【史】</note><app n="0134047"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">矩</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30817"/></rdg></app>古今。守<app type="star" corresp="#0134015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禁</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB13806"/></rdg></app>持浮。罹剎息心。每懼
<lb ed="I" n="0134b17" type="honorific"/>傷蘭。結草軀沉。雲昇<app type="star" corresp="#0134024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">佊</rdg></app>岸。與聖相尋。率<app type="star" corresp="#0134011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30789"/></rdg></app>令儁。裁捨己珍。同尊上道。剋像潛神。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b18" type="honorific"/>育<app type="star" corresp="#0134005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">王</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB24980"/></rdg></app>不並。須達豈申。抽靳截骨。早求出因。取石荊丘。雕彩<app type="star" corresp="#0134030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30801"/></rdg></app>章。<note n="0134048" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30818"/>＝圖【史】</note><note n="0134048" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30818"/>【佛拓】，圖【史】</note><app n="0134048"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30818"/></rdg></app>形真見。煥如
<lb ed="I" n="0134b19" type="honorific"/>故常。晌<g ref="#CB30782"/>鮮明。<app type="star" corresp="#0134029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">向</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30800"/></rdg></app><g ref="#CB30823"/>雜光。塵驚嚮應。風發鏘鏘。其下神龜。能聖復妖。形<app type="star" corresp="#0134032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">影</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30803"/></rdg></app>漢<app type="star" corresp="#0134034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">庭</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00527"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0134b20" type="honorific"/>夢感宋朝。置<app type="star" corresp="#0134002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">之</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02442"/></rdg></app>神川。宇宙照照。紀<note n="0134049" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30810"/>＝天【史】</note><note n="0134049" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30810"/>【佛拓】，天【史】</note><app n="0134049"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">天</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30810"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0134037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">綱</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30805"/></rdg></app>地。名遐遠霄。</p>
</cb:div>
